ZH: 1. 他穿着一件黑色的长袍。
EN: He is wearing a black robe.
ZH: 2. 她戴着一条红色的丝带束起了长袍。
EN: She tied up the robe with a red silk ribbon.
ZH: 3. 长袍是古代中国男子的传统服饰。
EN: The robe is a traditional attire for ancient Chinese men.
ZH: 4. 他披着一件华丽的金色长袍出席晚宴。
EN: He attended the banquet wearing a splendid golden robe.
ZH: 5. 这件长袍采用优质的丝绸制成。
EN: This robe is made of high-quality silk.
ZH: 6. 那个僧人穿着一件朴素的黑色袈裟长袍。
EN: The monk was wearing a plain black cassock robe.
ZH: 7. 这是一件印有精美图案的长袍。
EN: This is a robe adorned with exquisite patterns.
ZH: 8. 她用长袍裹住自己，躲避寒冷的冬风。
EN: She wrapped herself in a robe to shield from the cold winter wind.
ZH: 9. 长袍的颜色和纹饰反映着不同社会地位。
EN: The color and patterns on the robe reflect different social statuses.
ZH: 10. 这种长袍设计简洁而优雅。
EN: This type of robe is designed to be simple yet elegant.
ZH: 11. 他的长袍上绣着华丽的龙纹。
EN: His robe is embroidered with magnificent dragon patterns.
ZH: 12. 长袍在古代被认为是尊贵和地位的象征。
EN: The robe was considered a symbol of nobility and status in ancient times.
ZH: 13. 这件长袍是由著名设计师特制的。
EN: This robe is custom-made by a renowned designer.
ZH: 14. 他正在缝制一件华丽的长袍。
EN: He is currently sewing a splendid robe.
ZH: 15. 女巫穿着一件黑色的长袍，手持魔法法杖。
EN: The witch wore a black robe and held a magic wand.
ZH: 16. 这个角色扮演者穿着一件红色的僧衣长袍。
EN: The cosplayer was wearing a red monk robe.
ZH: 17. 长袍上的金边使它看起来更加庄重。
EN: The gold trim on the robe makes it look more solemn.
ZH: 18. 他将长袍披在肩上，向大厅走去。
EN: He draped the robe over his shoulders and walked towards the hall.
ZH: 19. 长袍的设计风格与时尚潮流息息相关。
EN: The design style of the robe is closely related to fashion trends.
ZH: 20. 这是一件柔软轻盈的长袍，穿着舒适。
EN: This is a soft and lightweight robe that is comfortable to wear.
